sd=Loan	This service domain handles the fulfillment of a general loan product. This includes the initial set-up of the loan facility and the completion of scheduled and ad-hoc product processing tasks	Example of use: An established and valued bank customer applies for and gets a loan for a home improvement project	The loan product represents a generic loan capability that may include different properties/features depending on a bank's preferences and policies. The loan may or may not be secured by collateral.
sdpath=loan
crpath=loan-fulfillment-arrangement
crr=Loan Fulfillment Arrangement Instance
mcr=Loan Fulfillment Arrangement
bqs=Interest ServiceFees Disbursement Maintenance Withdrawal Repayment Restructuring
CONFIG
LoanFulfillmentArrangement	initiate	Initiate a loan		initiateLoanFulfillmentArrangement		#desc
LoanFulfillmentArrangement	update	Update details for an existing loan		updateLoanFulfillmentArrangement		#desc
LoanFulfillmentArrangement	control	Control a loan (e.g. suspend, terminate)		controlLoanFulfillmentArrangement		#desc
LoanFulfillmentArrangement	retrieve	Retrieve details about a loan		retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangement		#desc
Interest	retrieve	Retrieve details about interest applied to a loan	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementInterest	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementInterest		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Interest instance related report
ServiceFees	execute	Execute a fee charge against a loan	executeLoanFulfillmentArrangementServiceFees	executeLoanFulfillmentArrangementServiceFees		Invoke an automated execute action against the Service Fees instance
ServiceFees	retrieve	Retrieve details about a loan fees	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementServiceFees	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementServiceFees		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Service Fees instance related report
Disbursement	retrieve	Retrieve details about a disbursement paid against a loan	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementDisbursement	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementDisbursement		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Disbursement instance related report
Maintenance	request	Request a maintenance activity for a consumer load (e.g. obtain a fee statement)	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementMaintenance	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementMaintenance		Invoke a service request action against the Maintenance instance
Maintenance	retrieve	Retrieve details about maintenance processing for a loan	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementMaintenance	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementMaintenance		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Maintenance instance related report
Withdrawal	update	Update details of a withdrawal from a loan	updateLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal	updateLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal		Update to any amendable fields of the Withdrawal instance
Withdrawal	execute	Execute an automated withdrawal against a loan	executeLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal	executeLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal		Invoke an automated execute action against the Withdrawal instance
Withdrawal	request	Request handling of a withdrawal (e.g. negotiate an exception)	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal		Invoke a service request action against the Withdrawal instance
Withdrawal	retrieve	Retrieve details about a loan withdrawal	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementWithdrawal		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Withdrawal instance related report
Repayment	update	Update a repayment transaction made to the loan	updateLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment	updateLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment		Update to any amendable fields of the Repayment instance
Repayment	execute	Execute an automated repayment transaction	executeLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment	executeLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment		Invoke an automated execute action against the Repayment instance
Repayment	request	Request handling of an exceptional repayment (e.g. a balloon repayment)	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment		Invoke a service request action against the Repayment instance
Repayment	retrieve	Retrieve details about a loan repayment	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment	retrieveLoanFulfillmentArrangementRepayment		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Repayment instance related report
Restructuring	initiate	Initiate loan account restructuring	initiateLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring	initiateLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring		Details of a new Restructuring instance
Restructuring	update	Update details of a loan or restructuring activities	updateLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring	updateLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring		Update to any amendable fields of the Restructuring instance
Restructuring	exchange	Accept, reject etc a loan restructuring proposal	exchangeLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring	exchangeLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring		Handle an external exchange (e.g. accept, reject, verify)
Restructuring	request	Request activity associated with a restructuring effort (e.g. negotiate)	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring	requestLoanFulfillmentArrangementRestructuring		Invoke a service request action against the Restructuring instance
